don't want to make it too much spicy so you

00:01:54.710 --> 00:02:05.710
can add half Chili or avoid it at all generally
Red Chilies are Sweet than the Green Chilies

00:02:05.710 --> 00:02:12.900
so you can add one chili but if you are using
green chili then you must be careful because

00:02:12.900 --> 00:03:13.469
it may be very hot, add these with the other
Ingredients, now chop the one Tomato, one

00:03:13.469 --> 00:03:40.700
